                      <item xml:id="e3"><desc>Numberer quires 1–2; a later hand has numbered quires 2–9.</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="e4"><desc>
                        Scribal intervention:
                        words of text are written interlinearly, <locus target="#4r #6r #6v #7r #8r" facs="009 011 012 012 013">folss. 4r, 6r, 6v, 7r, 8r, </locus>, etc.;
                        and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted, <locus target="#14v #36v #54r #76v #83r" facs="020 042 082 088">14v, 36v, 54r, 76v, 83r, </locus>,
                        and in another case where the symbol (+) is used, <locus target="#55v" facs="061">55v, </locus>;
                        erasure markings are visible, <locus target="#56v" facs="062">56v, </locus>;
                        text has been removed <locus target="#2r #3v #7r #9v #16r" facs="007 009 012 015 021">2r, 3v, 7r, 9v, 16r</locus>, etc.</desc></item>
                    </list>
                  </additions>

